Additional issues come into play with self quarantine for persons living alone, like depression and suicidal ideation.

When our President referred to the coronavirus as s HOAX and stated he had a HUNCH it would be gone with warm weather, we were already in TROUBLE. Stating his uncle went to MIT and is a Doctor gives the President no more insight into this epidemic than any person standing on the street corner.

Refusing the assistance of the World Health Organization shows an ego unwilling to accept a helping hand in the face of drowning. Has he even given thought to the millions of homeless who could be infected with this airborne disease? It is up to us as Americans to speak up and demand progress and legislation to protect our loved ones, families, friends and our Democracy before it is completely decimated through a loss of face and an unwillingness to be wrong.
